---
title: Chickpea and Beyond Meat® Shakshuka with Sesame Flatbreads and Feta
description: This dish — a breakfast staple in North Africa and parts of the Middle East — relies on tomatoes, peppers, eggs and a whole slew of spices. We've added chickpeas Beyond Meat® to this version for extra nutrition. Make sure you mop up every morsel with the nutty sesame flatbread!
